
## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Vivado generated directories
.Xil/
.cache/
.gen/
.hw/
.ip_user_files/
.runs/
.sim/

# Vivado generated files
*.jou
*.log
*.str
*.dcp
*.wdb
*.bit
*.bin
*.ltx

# Temporary and backup files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
*~

# Operating system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini